### 🔷 9. Specifications as Living Contracts

A specification is no longer static documentation. It is a **living contract** between human and AI:

- AI generates implementation from the spec
- Tests derive from acceptance criteria in the spec
- Documentation stays synchronized with the spec
- Changes propagate consistently when the spec updates

> **"In the era of Agents, your Spec is your Source Code."**

Golden Rule: If you can describe the excellence you want, AI can build the agent, skills, and MCP to deliver it.

